# Customer Behavior Analysis

## Introduction
This project aims to analyze customer behavior using a dataset of purchasing transactions. By leveraging SQL analytical functions, we can gain insights into customer patterns and behaviors, enabling us to target customers more efficiently, increase sales and revenue, improve customer retention, and reduce churn.

## Dataset
The dataset contains information about customer purchasing transactions. It includes data such as customer ID, transaction details, dates, and purchase amounts.

## Goals
The main objectives of this analysis are:
- Gain insights into customer behavior and preferences.
- Identify patterns and trends in customer purchasing habits.
- Segment customers based on their behavior and characteristics.
- Develop targeted marketing strategies and campaigns.
- Improve customer retention and reduce churn.
- Increase sales and revenue through personalized recommendations and offers.

